channel.title: Drum and bass drum loops
channel.description: Decided to make some dnb drum loops as I think Auxy 4.0 will be great for making dnb. So without using soundpacks, I made this loops! https://app.auxy.co/projects/OPwObTf47WIEg3eFLSHI6Q== I'd like to see what you do with these. To use them, copy the instrument containing the desired loop and paste it into a project. Feel free to edit any loops and change the instrument! Have fun!
